Kiva Mobile App
Coded by Willow Solem

Built on The M Project (http://www.the-m-project.org/)

=Setup=

Download and install The M Project (http://www.the-m-project.org/)

Install the Bower package manager
npm install bower -g

Install the Kiva SDK
bower install https://github.com/kiva/kiva.js.git
cd KivaApp/frameworks/kiva
ln -s ../../components/kiva.js/kiva.js kiva.js

Install the PhoneGap plugins
bower install https://github.com/purplecabbage/phonegap-plugins.git
bower install https://github.com/davejohnson/phonegap-plugin-facebook-connect.git
cd KivaApp/plugins/
cd plugins/ConnectPlugin/assets/
ln -s ../../../lib/phonegap-plugin-facebook-connect/www/cdv-plugin-fb-connect.js cdv-plugin-fb-connect.js
cd -
cd plugins/ConnectPlugin/src/org/apache/cordova/facebook/
ln -s ../../../lib/phonegap-plugin-facebook-connect/native/android/src/org/apache/cordova/facebook/ConnectPlugin.java ConnectPlugin.java
cd - 
cd plugins/GoogleAnalyticsTracker/assets/
ln -s ../../../lib/phonegap-plugins/Android/Analytics/2.0/www/analytics.js analytics.js
cd - 
cd plugins/GoogleAnalyticsTracker/src/com/phonegap/plugins/analytics/
ln -s ../../../lib/phonegap-plugins/Android/Analytics/2.0/src/com/phonegap/plugins/analytics/GoogleAnalyticsTracker.java GoogleAnalyticsTracker.java

Install Cordova (for using phonegap)
git clone https://github.com/phonegap/phonegap.git
mkdir lib/phonegap
cp path/to/phonegap/androidOrIos/cordova.js KivaApp/lib/phonegap 
mkdir frameworks/cordova
ln -s KivaApp/lib/phonegap/cordova.js KivaApp/frameworks/cordova/cordova.js

Run the Espresso server:
cd ../../..
espresso server

